                <h1>Can You Get a Background Check Before Turning 18?</h1>
                <p>Yes, individuals under 18 can undergo background checks, but the process is typically subject to local laws and the nature of the request. Generally, parental consent may be required. Background checks can help employers, schools, or organizations verify information such as criminal history or eligibility for specific programs.</p>
